text: Shopping secondhand helps address environmental and social issues by creating less waste and pollution and reducing harmful labor conditions that are generated by fast fashion clothing.
Shopping secondhand helps you to showcase your personal style by offering unique pieces that make you feel like you’ve uncovered a hidden gem compared to more generic fast fashion clothing.
Shopping secondhand helps your budget with affordable clothing that is less costly than new clothing.
